    evidence: "update.ts: added reconcileBlockedByDependency() + pre-mutate locateItem resolution; --blocked-by now adds a blocked_by dependency edge (mirrors create.ts), --unset blocked-by removes it, repoint replaces stale edge. Manual temp-dir smoke: edge_count 1 on set, 0 on clear. Added 3 regression tests to update-command.spec.ts (all green)."
