    created_at: "2026-05-23T03:44:21.336Z"
    updated_at: "2026-05-23T03:50:35.836Z"
    evidence: "close.ts: (C3) always scan active children; under validate-close off emit informational closed_with_active_children warning (never blocks). (C4) on terminal close clear scalar blocked_by + blocked_reason + blocked_by dependency edges (keeps kyd6 invariant), annotate via closed_cleared_blocked_by. Manual smoke verified both; 2 new regression tests; close-command.spec 11/11 green."
