    updated_at: "2026-05-23T03:55:03.504Z"
    evidence: "U2: root cause was LIST_FILTER_FLAG_CONTRACTS missing --status (the one gap vs pm list --help); added it so the existing never-block typo normalization now resolves --statuss->--status (consistent with all other list flags). U3: added --list option as alias for --explore on package/extension (register-setup.ts readBoolean(explore,list) + option + EXTENSION_FLAG_CONTRACTS entry). Tests: bootstrap-args U2 unit + cli.integration U3; both green. Manual smoke confirmed."
